'''Izragen''' niɣ '''Azragen''' ([[Tafransist]]: ''Erraguene'', [[Taɛrabt]]: ''إراقن ,إزراقن''), d yiwet taɣiwant n [[Tawilayt_n_Jijel|Tawilayt n Jijel]] g Tmurt Leqbayel. Imezdaɣ-ines, am wiha n [[Zyama Lmenṣuriya]], ihadren '''[[Tasaḥlit]]''' (Tamaziɣt) lwaḥi d '''[[Taɛrabt]]'''.  Taɣiwant n Izragen, tesɛa azal n 2,532 imezdaɣ deg useggwas n 2008. G luqt n listiɛmar llan qqarn-as ''"Merdj-Ez-Erraguene"''.

